<h1> Dalgona Coffee </h1>
<br>
 <img src="https://images.indianexpress.com/2020/03/dalgona-coffee-759.jpg" <br>
<br> <p1> <b>Ingredients<br></b>
</p1>
<p2> Milk <br>
  Coffee Powder <br>
  Sugar <br>
Hot Water <br>
  Ice Cubes <br>
</p2> 
 <br>
<br> <p3> <b> HOW TO MAKE!? </p3> <br>
  <br>
  <p4> <b>STEP 1 </b> <br> To Prepare this delecious Coffee, Take a bowl and Mix equal quantities of Coffee power and sugar and hot water.</p4> <br>
  <br>
  <br><b><p5> STEP 2 <br> Now, Using a blender, blend the coffee mixer until it is light, frothy, and creamy. It will take a good amount of time.</p5> <br>
  <br>
  <br>
  <p6> STEP 3 <br> Now, Take one glass or coffee mug and add ice cubes. pour cold milk in them and add this beaten wipped coffee over it. </p6> <br>
  <br>
  <p7> Now enjoy your Coffee </p7>

  <hr> My Mom's Recipe, Written by Tanav. </hr>



